\f0\b\fs34 \cf0 # Multi-Agent Research System\
\
An AI-powered multi-agent research assistant that automates web search, content extraction, report generation, and quality evaluation using Large Language Models (LLMs) and LangChain.\
\
## Features\
\
- \uc0\u55357 \u56589  Intelligent web search using Tavily Search API\
- \uc0\u55357 \u56516  Automatic webpage content extraction and cleaning\
- \uc0\u9997 \u65039  AI-generated structured research reports\
- \uc0\u55357 \u56541  Self-evaluation and critique of generated reports\
- \uc0\u55356 \u57104  Interactive Streamlit web interface\
- \uc0\u55358 \u56598  Modular multi-agent architecture built with LangChain\
\
